channel.title: RSMV being gay?
channel.description:
Ok so i was using rsmv to grab the models from runescapes recent cache. (655) And i have encountered a problem. It only sends request for model 262. [code] C:\Documents and Settings\Administrator\Desktop\Models\RSMV2>java Main Runescape Model Grabber Thanks to Silabsoft ~~~~~~~~~~ Grabbing Cache Version. Trying: 655 Accepted. ~~~~~~~~~~ Sending request for Model: 262 Model Grabbing Complete
C:\Documents and Settings\Administrator\Desktop\Models\RSMV2>pause Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
Why is it doing this? And is there a fix?
